╣THIS BENCH IS TO CELEBRATE
THE LIVES OF
WILF AND GLADYS BROWN
LANDLORD AND LANDLADY OF
"THE FAIR HOUSE" 1967 - 1979
WHO TOOK WITH THEM VERY SPECIAL
MEMORIES OF VERY SPECIAL PEOPLE"┐
╝A Bench was promised, a payment of sorts
to the Ladies of Astbury for all their support,
in helping me achieve my dream,
A Single Handicap Golfer in 2017
Jane Pickup..Living the Dream!"š
ęIn loving memory of Peter Maguire
A wonderful husband, dad & grandad
29th June 1945 - 1st July 2010
Just gone for a walk with the angels.

In loving memory of John James Maguire
A wonderful son, brother & uncle
24th April 1972 - 26th February 1994
You will never be forgotten and forever in our hearts

In loving memory of Heather Hayes
A devoted wife, mother & grandmother
7th July 1937 - 15th August 2004
Always in our thoughts, forever in our hearts."¶
